                        <interp inst="t18581213-name-295" type="surname" value="GISBY"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18581213-name-295" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS GISBY</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">City policeman</hi>, 245). I produce a certificate of the prisoner's former conviction (<hi rend="italic">Read: "Central Criminal Court, April, 1858; Robert Pierce convicted of embezzlement. Confined Four Months"</hi>)—the prisoner is the person.</p>
